---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import logo from "../assets/images/uniify/logo.svg";
import img1 from "../assets/images/uniify/create.png";
import img2 from "../assets/images/uniify/all.png";
import img3 from "../assets/images/uniify/profile.png";
import img4 from "../assets/images/uniify/drag.png";
import img5 from "../assets/images/uniify/lessons.png";
import img6 from "../assets/images/uniify/stripe.png";
---

<Layout title="uniify.ai | Project Page" navigation={false}>
  <main>
    <h2>UNIIFY.AI</h2>
    <h4 class="subheading">A global online learning platform.</h4>
    <div class="landing-section">
      <div class="info">
        <h4>the stack</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>React.js</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>Node.js</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>Mongo.DB</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>Typescript</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>Socket.io</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class={"technology"}>Stripe</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h4>about project</h4>
        <p>
          Through this project, I have demonstrated a high level of
          professionalism and proficiency in programming, ensuring a clean and
          organized codebase. The application of my UI/UX skills has resulted in
          a seamless and visually appealing user experience, showcasing my
          ability to create intuitive interfaces that prioritize user
          satisfaction.
        </p>
        <p>
          This substantial undertaking has not only expanded my technical
          capabilities but also fostered a deep appreciation for precision,
          attention to detail, and delivering exceptional outcomes. The lessons
          learned and skills acquired from this project have fortified my
          professional growth and equipped me with invaluable expertise that I
          am eager to apply in future endeavors.
        </p>
        <p>
          I am immensely proud of this project, as it stands as a testament to
          my commitment to excellence and my ability to tackle complex
          challenges with a disciplined and systematic approach.
        </p>
        <div class="btn-container">
          <button class="btn hoverable">
            <a class="external" href="https://uniify.ai/" target="_blank"
              >View live</a
            >
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <img class="logo" src={logo} alt="login" />
    </div>
    <h2>screenshots</h2>
    <div class="gallery">
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--1">
        <img src={img1} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 1" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--2">
        <img src={img2} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 2" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--3">
        <img src={img3} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 3" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--4">
        <img src={img4} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 4" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--5">
        <img src={img5} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 5" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="gallery__item gallery__item--6">
        <img src={img6} class="gallery__img" alt="Image 6" />
      </figure>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gallery {
    margin: 2rem 10rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .gallery__img {
    max-width: 40rem;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .external {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  ul {
    padding: 0;
  }
  li {
    display: inline-block;
  }
  li:not(:last-child) {
    margin-right: 1rem;
  }
  .landing-section {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    width: 80%;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 10rem;
    display: flex;
  }

  .logo {
    margin-left: 3rem;
    max-width: 30rem;
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .subheading {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .info {
    min-width: 25rem;
    max-width: 30rem;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    h2,
    h3,
    h4 {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .gallery {
      margin: 1rem;
    }
    .landing-section {
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;

      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 25rem;
    }
    .btn-container {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
